These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, motorbike, subway, tram, trike, jet-ski, airplane
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, cola, fanta, 7up, almond-milk, juice
7 different games are played: canasta, whist, snooker, domino, billiard, backgammon, scrabble
 1. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1
 2. the person playing whist is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 3. the person playing scrabble is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking water##2
 4. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person driving the bike is the person playing scrabble##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is between the person playing domino and the person driving the trike##2
 8. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
10. the person driving the airplane is the person drinking cola##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is the person driving the tram##1
12. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
13. the person playing canasta is the person drinking 7up##1
14. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person playing snooker and the person playing scrabble##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Transport   | trike | bike     | jet-ski | motorbike | tram | airplane  | subway  |
| Beverage   | water  | fanta        | lemonade  | juice     | almond-milk   | cola       | 7up   |
| Game         | whist   | scrabble | domino    | snooker  | billiard | backgammon | canasta |

