.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda, juice, iced-tea
House: modern, art-deco, colonial, townhouse, victorian, cape-cod, farmhouse
7 different games are played: domino, scrabble, monopoly, whist, mah-jongg, canasta, go
 1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 2. the victorian house is the victorian house##1
 3. the victorian house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 4. the townhouse house is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 5. the modern house is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is the person playing whist##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is between the farmhouse house and the person playing go##2
 8. the colonial house is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 9. the farmhouse house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
12. the person playing domino is the person drinking tea##1
13. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
14. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
15. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
16. the art-deco house is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage   | juice | iced-tea      | milk     | sprite  | mirinda | hot-chocolate | tea |
| House         | art-deco  | modern | cape-cod | colonial | farmhouse | townhouse   | victorian  |
| Game     | monopoly   | canasta     | go        | whist  | mah-jongg   | scrabble       | domino      |

