 6. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 7. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
12. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
13. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
14. the person watching superhero movies is the person traveling to miami##1
15. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1

