7 different pets are kept: fish, hedgehog, goat, rat, ferret, guinea-pig, chinchilla
 1. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1
 2. the cottage house is the person driving the taxi##1
 3. the owner of the goat is the wooden house##1
 4. the futuristic house is on the far right##1
 5. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 6. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
 7. the person driving the roller is in the middle##1
 8. the wooden house is on the left of the cottage house##1
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is the art-deco house##1
10. the owner of the fish is the person driving the motorbike##1
11. the townhouse house is the owner of the chinchilla##1
12. the person driving the subway is the owner of the ferret##1
13. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
14. the gothic-revival house is between the townhouse house and the wooden house##2
15. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3     |    4    |     5      |     6      |     7     |
