11. the person playing whist is the person who's birthday is in june##1
12. the fan ambient is on the far left##1
13. the person who's birthday is in february is the fan reggae##1
14. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
15. the fan dubstep is on the far right##1
16. the fan disco is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person playing whist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | electronic      | reggae | metal     | jazz     | disco   | dubstep |
| Birthday       | september    | november | february    | october | june     | march | august |
| Game        | mah-jongg    | canasta | monopoly    | poker    | whist | bridge | domino |

